In a message dated 3/11/03 6:29:00 AM Central Standard Time, 
cardhead649@... writes:


> "Awwww, does someone need a hug?" Empath taunts, having eavesdropped 
> on the conversation.

She stopped in mid motion, glancing back at Empath. She smirked then shook 
her feline head. 

"If you won't protest. Perhaps Teletran-1 in the Ark may be able to assist. 
That .. is where I am heading." Continuing, picking her way along the steep 
slope. Then, leaping down to the flat ground, glancing up at Empath. 

--part1_14a.1ce4dc74.2b9f5dc4_boundary
